Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.58,0:22:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think sad and painful things are pointless.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.83,0:22:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,If that's fate, then they must happen for a reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.06,0:22:04.68,Penguin_JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,それが運命なら　きっと意味がある
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.03,0:22:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I will accept it and become stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.54,0:22:07.07,Penguin_JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,あたしは受け入れて強くなるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.16,0:22:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,So...
